        public static Action partialAction(PlanSpace _space,
                                   Circumstance.Matcher prerequisite,
                                   Circumstance origin,
                                   Condition change,
                                   double cost)
        Forms a Partial Action, ie, an action that simpĺy changes one or more Conditins of an origin Circumstance and sets that as a result.
        Parameters:
        _space - The current Plan Space.
        prerequisite - The prerequisites to perform this new "Partial" Action.
        origin - The origin to change.
        change - The change to perform to the origin.
        cost - The cost of the new "Partial" Action.
        Returns:
        The new "Partial" Action. You can get the new node from Action.result.
